WEBVTT

00:00:06.835 --> 00:00:07.905
Na našoj planeti

00:00:07.905 --> 00:00:09.608
imamo dve polarne oblasti:

00:00:09.608 --> 00:00:11.370
Arktik, čije ime dolazi

00:00:11.370 --> 00:00:13.488
od grčke reči "arktikos" - severni,

00:00:13.488 --> 00:00:14.804
i Antarktik

00:00:14.804 --> 00:00:16.160
od "antarktikos" -

00:00:16.160 --> 00:00:17.726
suprotno od severnog.

00:00:17.726 --> 00:00:19.978
Ali postoji lakši način da se zapamte,

00:00:19.978 --> 00:00:22.082
ako se samo setite šta ih okružuje.

00:00:22.082 --> 00:00:25.749
Arktik, smešten na
severnoj hemisferi naše planete

00:00:25.749 --> 00:00:29.003
je okean, ceo okružen kopnom.

00:00:29.003 --> 00:00:30.547
Na drugoj strani sveta,